# /oss-flow — Open Source Hub Workflow

**Trigger:** Run ONLY when the user message is exactly `/oss-flow` or starts with `/oss-flow`. Otherwise ignore this rule.

Follow `~/.cursor/commands/oss-flow.md` in full. Hub: `OpenSource/` · JSON: `docs/assets/data/contributions.json` · Playbook: `WORKFLOW.md`

**Testing is mandatory before every push — miss nothing:**
- Upstream: all unit tests + edge cases + check/diff/idempotency per `<tech>/testing.md`
- Hub: full `npm run test:e2e` (96 tests, all projects) when JSON/site files change
- JSON sanity: stats, PR counts, timeline, meta.updated
- Manual smoke: preview, theme toggle, filters, links, mobile nav
- CI must be green after push — fix immediately if red

**Finish:** commit → push `main` → site live ~20s
